rclone-azureblob-airgap (1.73.2-15) unstable; urgency=high

  * systemd: pass mount config EXTRA_ARGS with systemd-compatible
    whitespace splitting (`$EXTRA_ARGS`) instead of unsupported shell default
    expansion so packaged rclone mount services no longer exit with usage
    status 2 when extra flags are configured.
  * tests: lock the systemd unit regression in test_release_hardening.py.
  * docs: document the systemd ExecStart argument handling rule.

