rclone-azureblob-airgap (1.73.2-3) unstable; urgency=high

  * systemd: remove ConditionPathIsDirectory=/run/rclone-azureblob/%i
    (RuntimeDirectory not yet created at condition evaluation time — service
    always failed to start with this condition).
  * systemd: use /usr/bin/rclone (actual deb install path) instead of
    /usr/local/bin/rclone (symlink) in ExecStart.
  * scripts/install.sh: fix shell syntax error in for-loop glob with
    redirect (bash syntax error on line 311).
  * debian/copyright: add missing copyright file (lintian E: no-copyright-file).
  * debian/rules: include both amd64+arm64 fuse-debs in each arch package
    (enables single deb to bootstrap any target arch in airgap scenario).
  * debian/rules: install lintian-overrides file.
  * debian/rclone-azureblob-airgap.lintian-overrides: suppress intentional
    lintian warnings (static binary, restricted permissions, systemctl calls).

